with the chicken, he didn't recognize me.

536
00:38:31,810 --> 00:38:33,479
It just did something to me.

537
00:38:36,190 --> 00:38:37,524
I understand.

538
00:38:37,608 --> 00:38:39,151
Finding it really hard.

539
00:38:40,736 --> 00:38:42,237
Come, give me a hug.

540
00:38:47,367 --> 00:38:49,495
