554
00:39:31,245 --> 00:39:32,120
Oh, nothing.

555
00:39:33,622 --> 00:39:34,456
Nothing.

556
00:39:55,519 --> 00:39:56,770
Everything all right?

557
00:39:58,480 --> 00:39:59,856
You had a good day?

558
00:39:59,940 --> 00:40:01,108
Yeah, very good.

559
00:40:01,817 --> 00:40:03,277
Laura came by.

560
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:05,487
Didn't she, Dad?
