561
00:40:05,571 --> 00:40:07,489
- Who?
- Laura.

562
00:40:07,573 --> 00:40:09,366
The young woman who came to see us.

563
00:40:13,203 --> 00:40:14,580
Then we saw the doctor.

564
00:40:14,663 --> 00:40:16,748
Has anyone seen my watch?
I seem to have lost it.

565
00:40:16,832 --> 00:40:17,874
Again?

566
00:40:18,625 --> 00:40:21,545
You've probably put it
in your cupboard. In your hiding place.

567
00:40:21,628 --> 00:40:22,713
What cupboard?

568
00:40:22,796 --> 00:40:26,091
I don't know what you're talking about.
I really don't know, Anne.

569
00:40:26,842 --> 00:40:29,845
What cupboard? There's no cupboard.
There's no cupboard, is there?

570
00:40:31,221 --> 00:40:32,639
Can we be more discreet?

571
00:40:32,723 --> 00:40:34,141
Have you looked in your cupboard?

572
00:40:34,224 --> 00:40:36,893
It's not there.
