573
00:40:36,977 --> 00:40:38,437
- Or it's been stolen.
- It hasn't.

574
00:40:38,520 --> 00:40:39,730
What do you mean, it hasn't?

575
00:40:39,813 --> 00:40:43,108
- It can't have flown away.
- You want me to go and have a look?

576
00:40:43,191 --> 00:40:44,818
Very much so. It is a bother.

577
00:40:44,901 --> 00:40:47,904
I am worried.
