00:42:17,869 --> 00:42:19,579
Yeah. Is it yours?

594
00:42:21,331 --> 00:42:24,000
I mean, is it yours?

595
00:42:24,751 --> 00:42:25,585
Yes.

596
00:42:26,628 --> 00:42:28,088
Might I see it?

597
00:42:28,171 --> 00:42:31,216
So, apparently, it went very well today.

598
00:42:31,299 --> 00:42:32,884
Oh, yes.

599
00:42:34,386 --> 00:42:35,762
Very well. Very well.

600
00:42:37,848 --> 00:42:39,766
Apparently, she looks like Lucy.

601
00:42:40,517 --> 00:42:41,601
Really?

602
00:42:42,519 --> 00:42:44,229
I don't know. I've never seen her.

603
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,356
No, it...

604
00:42:48,316 --> 00:42:50,902
It went well. Anne seemed pleased.
You know, it's...

605
00:42:50,986 --> 00:42:54,281
I don't really need--
It's mainly for Anne.

606
00:42:55,866 --> 00:42:57,617
Might I have a look at it?
See your watch?

607
00:42:57,701 --> 00:43:01,788
You're right, you know,
it's important to her this works out.

608
00:43:01,872 --> 00:43:02,873
Yeah.

609
00:43:04,166 --> 00:43:05,959
She's been worried about you.

610
00:43:06,042 --> 00:43:08,211
And it really upsets her

611
00:43:08,712 --> 00:43:10,797
when you keep falling out with--

612
00:43:13,550 --> 00:43:15,677
