613
00:43:15,761 --> 00:43:18,013
I was just looking.

614
00:43:18,096 --> 00:43:19,473
I want to check it's...

615
00:43:20,432 --> 00:43:23,393
Check if it's... It's pretty. Very pretty.

616
00:43:25,353 --> 00:43:26,313
Did you buy it?

617
00:43:26,396 --> 00:43:27,314
Sorry?

618
00:43:28,398 --> 00:43:30,525
Was it a present or did you buy it?

619
00:43:30,609 --> 00:43:31,485
I bought it.

620
00:43:32,319 --> 00:43:33,195
Why?

621
00:43:34,696 --> 00:43:36,323
I don't suppose you kept the receipt?

622
00:43:37,032 --> 00:43:38,492
What are you talking about?

623
00:43:38,575 --> 00:43:41,495
- Your watch. It's...
- I was talking about Anne.

624
00:43:43,288 --> 00:43:44,122
Anne?

625
00:43:45,999 --> 00:43:46,917
Yes, Anne.

626
00:43:48,043 --> 00:43:48,877
Yeah.

627
00:44:14,903 --> 00:44:17,572
I don't know why we never really
got on well together.

628
00:44:19,866 --> 00:44:21,535
Whereas her little sister...

629
00:44:22,285 --> 00:44:24,704
That was another story.

630
00:44:27,207 --> 00:44:29,793
Do you know her? She's marvelous.

631
00:44:30,710 --> 00:44:31,670
Marvelous.

632
00:44:32,587 --> 00:44:34,422
I haven't seen her for months.

633
00:44:37,384 --> 00:44:39,010
I can't blame her, she's...

634
00:44:39,886 --> 00:44:42,264
travelling around the world, I think.

635
00:44:43,181 --> 00:44:44,266
She's a painter.

636
00:44:47,352 --> 00:44:50,605
I'd be so happy
if she came to see me one day.

637
00:44:52,816 --> 00:44:57,279
I'd take her in my arms
and we'd be glued to one another.

638
00:44:58,738 --> 00:45:00,949
For hours on end, like we used to be.

639
00:45:01,783 --> 00:45:03,535
A long time ago, when she was little.

640
00:45:06,329 --> 00:45:09,249
When she still used to call me:

641
00:45:10,250 --> 00:45:11,334
"Little Daddy."

642
00:45:13,003 --> 00:45:14,045
"Little Daddy."

643
00:45:14,671 --> 00:45:15,547
Now, that's...

644
00:45:17,966 --> 00:45:19,885
That's what she used to call me.

645
00:45:21,177 --> 00:45:23,013
Nice, isn't it? "Little Daddy."

646
00:45:27,017 --> 00:45:28,560
Can I ask you a question?

647
00:45:31,688 --> 00:45:33,398
But I want an honest answer.

648
00:45:34,482 --> 00:45:35,775
Nothing fancy.

649
00:45:36,985 --> 00:45:38,361
Can you do that for me?

650
00:45:39,070 --> 00:45:39,905
Yeah.

651
00:45:42,866 --> 00:45:43,700
Well, then...

652
00:45:49,915 --> 00:45:53,001
How long do you intend to hang around here
