to start working here.

719
00:54:36,524 --> 00:54:40,278
- Would you like some more?
- I would. It's good chicken.

720
00:54:41,737 --> 00:54:44,031
Don't you think? Where did you buy it?

721
00:54:44,115 --> 00:54:45,324
