if you're doing it deliberately.

742
00:55:48,262 --> 00:55:49,138
What?

743
00:55:51,224 --> 00:55:52,350
Nothing.

744
00:55:57,104 --> 00:55:58,022
We had...

745
00:55:59,607 --> 00:56:01,692
