746
00:56:03,569 --> 00:56:05,321
But we had to cancel at the last moment.

747
00:56:05,404 --> 00:56:07,031
- Do you know why?
- No.

748
00:56:07,698 --> 00:56:09,617
Because of your row with Angela.

749
00:56:10,535 --> 00:56:12,662
