764
00:57:08,509 --> 00:57:12,430
- No, you don't understand.
- I do. But what I don't understand is...

765
00:57:13,764 --> 00:57:16,225
You do so much for him,

766
00:57:16,309 --> 00:57:19,020
and I respect you for that.

767
00:57:19,103 --> 00:57:22,523
I mean, you took the decision
to bring him here and...

768
00:57:23,107 --> 00:57:25,067
You know, why not? But...

769
00:57:27,820 --> 00:57:29,238
How can I put this?

770
00:57:29,822 --> 00:57:32,617
I think you have to come up
with a different solution.

771
00:57:32,700 --> 00:57:34,910
- He's totally lost it.
- Stop talking like that.

772
00:57:34,994 --> 00:57:37,705
